node.text:
The all new @jacobandco’s impressive Chiron Tourbillon in 7 different gemstones iterations.
This watch took almost 1 year to develop and it consists of 578 components.
The Chiron Tourbillon skills feature a case that houses a very complicated movement with a 1-minute 30° inclined flying tourbillon, the ”W16 Engine” in a sapphire block and a Power Reserve indicator. The addition of gemstones are the cherry on the top and give a touch of unmistakable flair👨‍🎨
A true engine on the wrist.
